624
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:03,100
What can he do?

625
00:36:03,540 --> 00:36:05,140
Don't underestimate him.

626
00:36:05,700 --> 00:36:06,740
He is clever.

627
00:36:07,660 --> 00:36:09,020
I've never feared anyone.

628
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:10,660
Cheung-wing, leave him to me

629
00:36:10,860 --> 00:36:12,020
