630
00:36:12,020 --> 00:36:13,540
Calm down.

631
00:36:15,060 --> 00:36:16,420
I've got another task for you.

632
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,260
What is it?

633
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:20,500
Starting tomorrow,

634
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:22,140
shadow Uncle.

635
00:36:22,540 --> 00:36:23,860
Whatever he does,

636
00:36:23,860 --> 00:36:25,060
let me know immediately.

637
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:27,900
A guy again?

638
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:29,380
And an old one.

639
00:36:31,940 --> 00:36:33,060
What's the plan?

640
00:36:33,260 --> 00:36:35,340
There won't be
any fighting or bloodshed,

641
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:37,140
and you can make big money.

642
00:36:37,660 --> 00:36:38,580
Sounds good?

643
00:36:41,820 --> 00:36:42,940
Great!

644
00:36:42,940 --> 00:36:44,100
We cut the roast pig

645
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:45,580
to wish everyone

646
00:36:45,780 --> 00:36:46,540
peace and prosperity!

647
00:36:46,540 --> 00:36:48,020
Great!

648
00:36:48,620 --> 00:36:49,140
All right,

649
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:49,900
please sit down.

650
00:36:51,820 --> 00:36:52,940
Everyone

651
00:36:53,180 --> 00:36:55,020
from the old town,

652
00:36:55,340 --> 00:36:57,420
Uncle Chen has tossed
the moon blocks three times

653
00:36:57,700 --> 00:36:59,700
in front of the Hung Shing Temple,

654
00:36:59,700 --> 00:37:01,180
and all of them are laughing answers.

655
00:37:01,940 --> 00:37:02,580
So,

656
00:37:02,580 --> 00:37:03,980
by the will of the deity

657
00:37:04,140 --> 00:37:06,420
and in my role
as Area Committee Chairman

658
00:37:06,620 --> 00:37:08,060
I declare that we oppose selling off

659
00:37:08,060 --> 00:37:09,380
any land in the old town.

660
00:37:09,380 --> 00:37:11,420
That's right!

661
00:37:11,420 --> 00:37:12,620
To this day,

662
00:37:12,860 --> 00:37:15,700
the old town is the last part of Hokong

663
00:37:15,700 --> 00:37:17,780
that preserves
its centuries-old character.

664
00:37:18,340 --> 00:37:20,420
We cannot allow

665
00:37:20,420 --> 00:37:21,380
unscrupulous property developers

666
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:23,020
to ruin the old town.

667
00:37:23,020 --> 00:37:26,100
Well said!

668
00:37:26,500 --> 00:37:27,940
The land of the old town

669
00:37:28,100 --> 00:37:29,900
is the root left to us by our ancestors.

670
00:37:30,300 --> 00:37:31,980
We will not yield an inch.

671
00:37:31,980 --> 00:37:33,740
Not an inch!

672
00:37:34,020 --> 00:37:36,340
If anyone dares to trample on our home,

673
00:37:36,340 --> 00:37:38,020
we will unite

674
00:37:38,260 --> 00:37:39,220
and fight to the very end.

675
00:37:39,220 --> 00:37:43,220
Fight to the very end!

676
00:37:43,220 --> 00:37:44,060
All right.

677
00:37:44,060 --> 00:37:45,380
Let me add to that.

678
00:37:46,060 --> 00:37:47,500
The land deeds of the old town

679
00:37:47,700 --> 00:37:50,500
