00:38:11,180 --> 00:38:12,300
Yes, I want that one.

691
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:13,460
Yes, that one.

692
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:19,700
So,

693
00:38:19,980 --> 00:38:22,180
