694
00:38:22,700 --> 00:38:24,940
What did you do really?

695
00:38:25,140 --> 00:38:27,180
All three throws of the blocks
came up as laughing answers.

696
00:38:30,780 --> 00:38:32,020
The deity's secrets
must not be revealed.

697
00:38:34,860 --> 00:38:35,580
Cheung-wing,

698
00:38:35,780 --> 00:38:36,900
now that the business is done,

699
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:38,860
shouldn't we have
a little entertainment

700
00:38:38,860 --> 00:38:39,820
as a reward?

701
00:38:40,060 --> 00:38:40,580
Okay.

702
00:38:41,460 --> 00:38:43,060
I'll take you to something thrilling.

703
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:51,460
Didn't expect it, huh?

704
00:38:52,180 --> 00:38:53,540
We both survived.

705
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:55,980
So is it my good luck

706
00:38:56,420 --> 00:38:57,820
